# Halo/Cloud Profile Parameter 
# ===============================================================================================================
Cloud_CenterX             48e3                          # central x coordinate in [48e3]
Cloud_CenterY             48e3                          # central y coordinate in [48e3]
Cloud_CenterZ             48e3                          # central z coordinate in [48e3]
Cloud_MaxR                36000.0                       # Maximum radius for the particle [36000.0] 
Cloud_Rho0                0.001976013787                # Maximum core density for the cloud [0.001976013787]
Cloud_R0                  6081.0                        # Maximum core radius for the cloud/halo [6081.0]
# ===============================================================================================================

# Bulk Velocity of the Halo/Cloud : These will be updated when running GAMER, so no adjustment needed 
Cloud_BulkVelX            0.000000                      
Cloud_BulkVelY            -0.003605                     
Cloud_BulkVelZ            0.000000                      

Cloud_MassProfNBin        1000                          # number of radial bins in the mass profile table [1000]
Cloud_Par_Num_Ratio       1.0                           # particle number ratio [1.0]
Cloud_RSeed               123                           # random seed for setting particle position and velocity (>=0) [123]


Cloud_Type	          Table                         # SHOULD NOT be modified, if one wants to change the halo/cloud type, please see "HALO_TYPE" [Table]
Density_Table_Name        Profile_Table                 # The table name which contains the radius, density and enclosed mass information. [Profile_Table]
